### Register User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Testing User",
    "email": "test_api@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login User
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test_api@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

###

### Cek Current User
# Pastikan server berjalan dan ganti <masukkan_token_dari_login_di_sini> dengan token dari response login.
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/current
Authorization: Bearer 357a039b-d192-4c30-be7d-8335b71064b1
